content.name: Git clean all
content.cmdStr: git checkout . && git reset . && git clean -df

Fechar bug

content.cmdStr:
xmo-client -p Device/Bridging/Bridges/Bridge[@uid='1']/Ports/Port[@uid='5']/Enable -s false
xmo-client -p Device/Ethernet/Interfaces/Interface[@uid='4']/Role -s WAN
xmo-client -p Device/Ethernet/Links/Link[@uid='2']/LowerLayers -s "Device/Ethernet/Interfaces/Interface[PHY4]"
xmo-client -p Device/Ethernet/Links/Link[@uid='3']/LowerLayers -s "Device/Ethernet/Interfaces/Interface[PHY4]"
xmo-client -p Device/Optical/Interfaces/Interface[@uid='1']/Enable -s false

content.name: Git checkout (uncleaned)
content.cmdStr: git checkout . && git reset . && git clean -df && git checkout ${BranchName}

content.name: Git Checkout branch updated
content.cmdStr: git checkout . && git reset . && git clean -df && git checkout ${BranchName:master} && git pull

content.name: Git squash N
content.cmdStr: git reset --soft HEAD~${Number:1} && git add . && git commit -m "${NovaMensagem}"
